  "text": "Among ligands, the most highly expressed were BMP2 and BMP6 (Fig. 1b) . Synoviocytes also expressed specific RNAs for the Smad signal transducers, Smad1, Smad5, and the common partner Smad4, as well as the well-known BMP target genes, the Id protein family and Runx transcription factors [CITATION_1] (Fig. 1c, d ).",
